original_query: What does markitdown say about Plugins?
solution_summary: Markitdown supports 3rd-party plugins, disabled by default. List installed plugins with `markitdown --list-plugins`. Enable plugins with `markitdown --use-plugins path-to-file.pdf`. Find plugins on GitHub using `#markitdown-plugin`. Develop plugins using `packages/markitdown-sample-plugin`.

steps.description: Since the previous step was succesful, conclude with the information gathered.
